as the one you drew last time.

3
00:00:27,940 --> 00:00:29,740
You even notice stuff like that?

4
00:00:30,480 --> 00:00:32,680
I thought you knew nothing about these.

5
00:00:35,590 --> 00:00:36,990
Don't underestimate me.

6
00:00:41,030 --> 00:00:41,950
You know what?

7
00:00:45,530 --> 00:00:47,260
Everything about you

8
00:00:48,230 --> 00:00:49,990
is documented in my head.

9
00:01:04,459 --> 00:01:05,390
Is someone here?

10
00:01:07,430 --> 00:01:08,720
I think it's Soyu.

11
00:01:09,840 --> 00:01:10,660
Soyu?

12
00:01:11,200 --> 00:01:12,370
You know, my senior

13
00:01:12,610 --> 00:01:14,670
who invited me to her birthday party.

14
00:01:15,160 --> 00:01:17,160
I think I texted her this address.

15
00:01:20,980 --> 00:01:22,430
I want to tell her

16
00:01:23,010 --> 00:01:24,630
about our relationship

17
00:01:26,450 --> 00:01:28,090
and who I'm with.

18
00:01:30,500 --> 00:01:31,520
Let's

19
00:01:31,640 --> 00:01:32,310
hide,

20
00:01:33,039 --> 00:01:35,039
and then scare her.

21
00:01:35,400 --> 00:01:36,400
What do you think?

22
00:01:41,850 --> 00:01:42,700
OK.

23
00:01:43,520 --> 00:01:44,920
I'll play along with you.

24
00:01:45,520 --> 00:01:46,050
Let's go.

25
00:01:46,200 --> 00:01:46,729
Let's go.

26
00:01:48,650 --> 00:01:49,250
Your hand.

27
00:01:50,280 --> 00:01:50,880
Your hand!

28
00:01:51,400 --> 00:01:51,930
Let's go.

29
00:01:52,820 --> 00:01:55,220
-Let's go over there.
-Let's go over there.

30
00:02:04,260 --> 00:02:05,680
Merry Christmas!

31
00:02:12,480 --> 00:02:14,380
Haejun, I'm here.

32
00:02:18,030 --> 00:02:20,030
Haejun, are you home?

33
00:03:07,340 --> 00:03:08,290
Haejun!

34
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:10,860
Haejun, are you upstairs?

35
00:03:37,220 --> 00:03:38,190
Over there!

36
00:03:38,470 --> 00:03:39,750
What? We should go that way!

37
00:03:39,750 --> 00:03:40,370
Over there.

38
00:03:40,370 --> 00:03:41,030
Over there.

39
00:03:41,050 --> 00:03:41,710
Over there.

40
00:03:50,260 --> 00:03:51,400
Move inside. Hurry.

41
00:03:51,590 --> 00:03:51,970
What?

42
00:04:06,160 --> 00:04:07,010
Haejun.

43
00:04:07,830 --> 00:04:08,900
Are you upstairs?

44
00:04:10,640 --> 00:04:12,700
Is he playing hide-and-seek with me?

45
00:04:16,510 --> 00:04:17,839
Are you uncomfortable?

46
00:04:18,209 --> 00:04:18,850
No.

47
00:04:18,850 --> 00:04:19,630
I'm fine.

48
00:04:53,090 --> 00:04:53,600
Stop it!

49
00:05:07,180 --> 00:05:08,430
Hello?

50
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:10,320
Yes, yes.

51
00:05:10,500 --> 00:05:12,180
OK, I'll be right there.

52
00:05:19,830 --> 00:05:20,760
I think she left.

53
00:05:21,730 --> 00:05:23,930
I thought my heart was going to explode!

54
00:05:24,370 --> 00:05:25,970
She's gone. Let's continue.

55
00:05:27,810 --> 00:05:28,730
No.

56
00:05:28,730 --> 00:05:30,730
Don't you think we're childish?

57
00:05:31,290 --> 00:05:31,790
No.

58
00:05:32,430 --> 00:05:33,800
We're adults.

59
00:06:13,630 --> 00:06:15,630
-Cheers.
-Cheers.

60
00:06:26,370 --> 00:06:27,340
I knew it.

61
00:06:28,390 --> 00:06:30,390
Such wine is not for me.

62
00:06:32,330 --> 00:06:34,260
This is from Kang Soohyung, right?

63
00:06:35,400 --> 00:06:37,400
It's made in Spain, and aged too.

64
00:06:38,850 --> 00:06:39,850
By the way,

65
00:06:40,650 --> 00:06:42,650
do rich people really drink this?

66
00:06:43,180 --> 00:06:45,180
It's expensive and tastes awful.

67
00:06:46,860 --> 00:06:48,010
Who was the one

68
00:06:48,570 --> 00:06:51,050
who said he wanted
to have a drink to go with

69
00:06:51,400 --> 00:06:52,530
the Christmas mood?

70
00:06:52,860 --> 00:06:54,390
I thought it'd taste sweet.

71
00:06:55,440 --> 00:06:57,810
Sigh, I should've just had some juice.

72
00:06:58,860 --> 00:07:00,160
I want Coke too.

73
00:07:04,070 --> 00:07:05,280
Open your mouth.

74
00:07:11,410 --> 00:07:12,210
Hey.

75
00:07:14,830 --> 00:07:15,440
Do you

76
00:07:15,510 --> 00:07:16,840
believe in Santa Claus?

77
00:07:19,770 --> 00:07:20,920
How old are you?

78
00:07:21,460 --> 00:07:22,990
You still believe in Santa?

79
00:07:23,520 --> 00:07:24,950
My mom said

80
00:07:26,800 --> 00:07:28,200
if you really want it,

81
00:07:28,750 --> 00:07:30,130
it will come true.

82
00:07:33,930 --> 00:07:34,610
Then,

83
00:07:36,610 --> 00:07:37,700
at this moment,

84
00:07:38,520 --> 00:07:39,450
what do you want?

85
00:07:41,280 --> 00:07:41,880
I...

86
00:07:43,770 --> 00:07:45,630
want to spend Christmas with you.

87
00:07:47,010 --> 00:07:48,870
Sit in front of the Christmas tree

88
00:07:49,520 --> 00:07:51,450
and have delicious food together,

89
00:07:52,500 --> 00:07:54,159
and give each other presents.

90
00:07:55,360 --> 00:07:56,610
Merry Christmas.

91
00:08:01,840 --> 00:08:03,500
It'll continue to be like this

92
00:08:04,820 --> 00:08:05,620
in the future.

93
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:08,760
Merry Christmas.

94
00:08:18,950 --> 00:08:19,880
This is for you.

95
00:08:26,580 --> 00:08:27,800
Can I open it now?

96
00:08:28,510 --> 00:08:29,010
Yes.

97
00:08:29,450 --> 00:08:30,390
Of course.

98
00:08:39,510 --> 00:08:40,740
You know what?

99
00:08:41,770 --> 00:08:43,169
You look like a Chihuahua

100
00:08:43,530 --> 00:08:45,130
waiting to be fed his snacks.

101
00:08:45,620 --> 00:08:47,170
Don't change the subject.

102
00:09:05,620 --> 00:09:06,790
It's a scarf.

103
00:09:08,020 --> 00:09:09,150
I knitted it myself.

104
00:09:10,510 --> 00:09:12,240
I was really worried

105
00:09:12,240 --> 00:09:13,440
you wouldn't like it.

106
00:09:17,140 --> 00:09:18,160
Of course not.

107
00:09:24,270 --> 00:09:26,000
I like it because it's from you.

108
00:09:26,430 --> 00:09:27,180
No.

109
00:09:28,380 --> 00:09:29,400
I like it the most

110
00:09:30,220 --> 00:09:31,480
because it's from you.

111
00:09:44,780 --> 00:09:46,040
This is my gift for you.

112
00:09:49,250 --> 00:09:49,820
Is this

113
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:51,870
an air ticket?

114
00:09:54,400 --> 00:09:55,210
Is it mine?

115
00:09:57,800 --> 00:09:59,930
You always said you wanted to go there.

116
00:10:00,670 --> 00:10:01,730
Let's go together.

117
00:10:10,540 --> 00:10:12,040
Is it too sudden?

118
00:10:12,500 --> 00:10:13,230
If you don't want to go,

119
00:10:13,230 --> 00:10:14,090
I'll cancel it.

120
00:10:15,110 --> 00:10:15,810
No.

121
00:10:16,700 --> 00:10:18,430
It's not that I don't want to go,

122
00:10:18,600 --> 00:10:20,260
but it's too expensive a gift.

123
00:10:24,440 --> 00:10:25,700
Every cent spent on you

124
00:10:26,300 --> 00:10:27,400
is worth it.

125
00:11:23,680 --> 00:11:25,450
It's snowing so heavily.

126
00:12:01,140 --> 00:12:01,840
Haejun.

127
00:12:04,110 --> 00:12:05,440
Let's do something fun.

128
00:12:11,530 --> 00:12:12,460
Close your eyes.

129
00:12:32,710 --> 00:12:33,330
Look.

130
00:12:36,480 --> 00:12:37,750
Where did you get this?

131
00:12:38,040 --> 00:12:39,370
It's so beautiful.

132
00:12:47,870 --> 00:12:48,620
This is

133
00:12:48,940 --> 00:12:49,940
a Christmas tree.

134
00:12:50,360 --> 00:12:51,830
Draw something else.

135
00:13:08,000 --> 00:13:09,280
Look at this.

136
00:13:15,690 --> 00:13:16,710
Haejun.

137
00:13:20,500 --> 00:13:21,100
I love you.

138
00:13:24,730 --> 00:13:25,300
Me too.

139
00:13:33,070 --> 00:13:33,720
Jaehun.

140
00:13:37,610 --> 00:13:38,870
They say the New Year is

141
00:13:40,750 --> 00:13:43,280
the day the Earth enters a new cycle

142
00:13:44,950 --> 00:13:47,350
under the influence
of the moon and the sun.

143
00:13:49,790 --> 00:13:51,060
That's just like us.

144
00:13:57,090 --> 00:13:57,910
I feel

145
00:13:59,490 --> 00:14:01,100
so blessed and excited

146
00:14:02,820 --> 00:14:04,100
to welcome the New Year

147
00:14:05,350 --> 00:14:06,230
with you.

148
00:15:13,630 --> 00:15:14,530
Look!

149
00:15:38,470 --> 00:15:39,350
Kim Haejun!

150
00:15:42,260 --> 00:15:43,030
Yeah?

151
00:16:16,110 --> 00:16:18,040
That was a Christmas gift.

152
00:16:20,380 --> 00:16:21,640
This is a New Year gift.

153
00:16:42,250 --> 00:16:44,580
The Christmas gift is for the present you.

154
00:16:46,810 --> 00:16:48,030
This New Year gift

155
00:16:49,880 --> 00:16:51,230
is for the future you.

156
00:17:02,930 --> 00:17:04,329
This is my promise to you.

157
00:17:10,069 --> 00:17:11,470
With this ring,

158
00:17:13,780 --> 00:17:14,710
I'm promising

159
00:17:16,210 --> 00:17:18,210
to go into the future with you.

160
00:17:32,220 --> 00:17:34,220
You didn't ask for my consent.

161
00:17:36,400 --> 00:17:38,130
No need for consent or refusal.

162
00:17:42,790 --> 00:17:43,620
When you said

163
00:17:44,840 --> 00:17:46,840
you wanted to be with me,

164
00:17:48,380 --> 00:17:51,580
when you said you wanted to
spend every Christmas with me,

165
00:17:52,580 --> 00:17:54,240
you'd made your promise to me.

166
00:19:13,720 --> 00:19:14,900
No!

167
00:19:29,660 --> 00:19:31,190
This is just the beginning.

168
00:19:55,620 --> 00:19:56,770
This is the first

169
00:19:58,350 --> 00:19:59,550
New Year gift from me.

170
00:22:06,150 --> 00:22:06,980
You're awake.

171
00:22:10,990 --> 00:22:12,290
Let's have breakfast.

172
00:22:14,790 --> 00:22:16,120
I'm still in dreamland.

173
00:22:18,550 --> 00:22:19,680
Still in dreamland?

174
00:22:21,300 --> 00:22:22,700
Let me wake you up.

175
00:22:26,230 --> 00:22:27,890
Why are you so energetic?

176
00:22:31,880 --> 00:22:33,020
Because

177
00:22:34,860 --> 00:22:36,420
this is the first New Year

178
00:22:37,480 --> 00:22:38,760
I'm spending with you.

179
00:22:42,040 --> 00:22:45,970
I wanted to wake you up earlier
to welcome the new year together sooner.

180
00:22:47,890 --> 00:22:48,710
From now on,

181
00:22:53,140 --> 00:22:54,490
let's spend

182
00:22:57,690 --> 00:22:59,230
every year together here.

183
00:23:06,090 --> 00:23:07,190
Really?

184
00:23:12,340 --> 00:23:13,000
It's a deal.

185
00:23:20,550 --> 00:23:21,670
Deal.

186
00:23:31,690 --> 00:23:32,900
From now on,

187
00:23:35,000 --> 00:23:36,860
let's spend every year together.

188
00:24:56,890 --> 00:25:04,680
[Tide of Love 2]

189
00:26:03,010 --> 00:26:11,520
[Tide of Love 2]
